        <hl1>How Black Comedy Got the Last Laugh</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Mark D Miller letter on Lynn Hirschberg's September 3 article holds new comedians are getting so good that studio heads and network executives no longer se black, they see green (S)</p>
      </abstract>
