    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>These new comedians like Chris Tucker and Chris Rock are good and getting better, so good in fact that studio heads and network executives no longer see black -- they see green.</p>
        <p>Mark D. Miller  Sherman Oaks, Calif.</p>
